<sect1 id="app-pgreceivexlog" xreflabel="pg_receivexlog">

  <title><command>pg_receivexlog</command> 重命名为 <command>pg_receivewal</command></title>

   <indexterm>
     <primary>pg_receivexlog</primary>
     <see>pg_receivewal</see>
   </indexterm>

   <para>
    PostgreSQL 9.6 及以下版本提供了名为<command>pg_receivexlog</command><indexterm><primary>pg_receivexlog</primary></indexterm>的命令，用于获取预写式日志（WAL）文件。该命令已重命名为<command>pg_receivewal</command>；关于<command>pg_receivewal</command>的文档，请参见<xref linkend="app-pgreceivewal"/>；关于这一变更的详情，请参见<link linkend="release-prior">PostgreSQL 10 的发布注释</link>。
   </para>

</sect1>
